#grids.section
  .col
    h1 Grids
    hr
    div
      | We use 
      code inline-blocks
      |  for columns.
    div
      |  In that way we preventing common problem of all float grids: 
      a(href='http://stackoverflow.com/questions/30598970/bootstrap-row-elements-with-variable-height', target='_blank') variable columns height.
    div 
      |For example, Bootstrap trying to fix it in a
      a(href="http://getbootstrap.com.vn/examples/equal-height-columns/", target="_blank") flexbox-way 
    div But this solution works only on less-than-12 columns per row. Flexbox just shrinks all colunns into a single row. 
    div Also 
      code flexbox
      |  have a lot of issues on IE 10 & 11.      
    
    
