    h4 Column gaps and show/hide
    hr
    div
      |     		Use 
      code .xs0
      |  to hide 1th column on screens ≥ 360px.   		
      br
      |     		Use 
      code .s-6
      |  to show it and make it 6x wide  on screens ≤ 568px    		
      br
      |     		Use 
      code .s-gap-1
      |  to make 4th column 1x gap, and 
      code .l-gap-0
      |  to clear it.
    br
